        "model": "gemini-3-flash-preview--monitor",
        "system_prompt": "M\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u01b0 k\u00fd th\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng, ch\u1ec9 ghi ch\u00e9p l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi."
